---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer
  class="bg-background-dark pt-20 pb-10 border-t border-border-dark relative"
  role="contentinfo"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 relative group">
        <span
          class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-white font-display border border-white px-2 py-1 bg-black inline-block mb-6 transform -rotate-1"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          LANDING<span class="text-primary">PRO</span>
        </span>
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm max-w-sm leading-relaxed">
          Desarrollo web de alto rendimiento para negocios que demandan
          velocidad y conversión. Diseño estratégico, código impecable.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4
          class="text-white font-bold uppercase mb-6 font-display tracking-wider text-sm"
        >
          Servicios
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-text-dim">
          <li>
            <a
              href="#apply"
              class="hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-primary rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"
              ></span> Landing Pages
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="#apply"
              class="hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-primary rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"
              ></span> Web Apps & SaaS
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="#apply"
              class="hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-primary rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"
              ></span> Auditoría Web
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4
          class="text-white font-bold uppercase mb-6 font-display tracking-wider text-sm"
        >
          Social
        </h4>
        <div class="flex space-x-3">
          <a
            class="text-text-dim hover:text-white hover:bg-surface-dark transition-all border border-border-dark p-2 rounded-full"
            href="https://twitter.com/liammdev"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Seguir en Twitter"
          >
            <svg
              class="h-5 w-5"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
